Comment: 1,0:06:07.85,0:06:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Comment: 1,0:06:09.80,0:06:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Comment: 1,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Comment: 1,0:01:10.20,0:01:11.75,orig,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Comment: 1,0:01:11.75,0:01:13.30,orig,,0,0,0,,Everyone's happy with your cooking.
Comment: 1,0:01:27.30,0:01:27.90,orig,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 1,0:01:54.00,0:01:54.65,orig,,0,0,0,,Just right.
Comment: 1,0:03:59.90,0:04:02.05,orig,,0,0,0,,How does a wall just break?
Comment: 1,0:04:02.40,0:04:05.70,orig,,0,0,0,,How the heck am I supposed to know?
Comment: 1,0:04:12.30,0:04:16.35,orig,,0,0,0,,You were trying to, and that's a crime! I'll call the police!
Comment: 1,0:04:25.75,0:04:27.20,orig,,0,0,0,,How do you know we brought our towels?
Comment: 1,0:04:38.70,0:04:44.05,orig,,0,0,0,,Tell the truth. I won't get mad if you say it now.
Comment: 1,0:07:07.45,0:07:08.60,orig,,0,0,0,,So what's the plan?
Comment: 1,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.45,orig,,0,0,0,,What plan?
Comment: 1,0:07:16.25,0:07:16.75,orig,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Comment: 1,0:07:17.30,0:07:17.80,orig,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Comment: 1,0:07:24.80,0:07:25.75,orig,,0,0,0,,It happens to you sometimes.
Comment: 1,0:08:57.70,0:09:02.72,orig,,0,0,0,,The guys have been getting by going commando, but what about the girls?
Comment: 1,0:09:27.10,0:09:29.25,orig,,0,0,0,,Oh... I'm, uh...
Comment: 1,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.75,orig,,0,0,0,,Th-This isn't good. I'll really be on the same level as Ranta—
Comment: 1,0:09:48.75,0:09:50.25,orig,,0,0,0,,Huh? Nothing.
Comment: 1,0:10:51.70,0:10:57.80,orig,,0,0,0,,Damuro was much bigger than Ortana, and is now a base for goblins.
Comment: 1,0:12:34.90,0:12:35.90,orig,,0,0,0,,Don't celebrate yet.
Comment: 1,0:12:36.40,0:12:37.85,orig,,0,0,0,,We need to keep this up.
Comment: 1,0:13:30.85,0:13:32.90,orig,,0,0,0,,The mood lightened again.
Comment: 1,0:15:37.70,0:15:38.80,orig,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Comment: 1,0:16:13.30,0:16:14.50,orig,,0,0,0,,Forget about being influenced.
Comment: 1,0:17:14.90,0:17:15.60,orig,,0,0,0,,I see.
Comment: 1,0:17:33.80,0:17:38.00,orig,,0,0,0,,we could have clothes for wearing\Nindoors, too, wouldn't that be nice?
Comment: 1,0:17:55.30,0:17:55.90,orig,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Comment: 1,0:18:22.75,0:18:23.35,orig,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 1,0:18:46.64,0:18:47.14,orig,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Comment: 1,0:19:13.85,0:19:14.35,orig,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Comment: 1,0:20:22.40,0:20:26.45,orig,,0,0,0,,I don't think I like that kind of thing, to ask for favors.

Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.25,0:00:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Moguzo, they had them.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:39.20,0:00:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Breakfast will be a feast.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.45,0:00:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You really like cooking, huh.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.30,0:00:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not even on breakfast duty.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.00,0:00:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like making or eating food better?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.20,0:00:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.60,0:00:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.70,0:01:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I like both, I guess.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.35,0:01:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I liked cooking for people.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.75,0:01:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Aside from whether or not it made them happy.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.35,0:01:11.75,fix,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.75,0:01:13.30,fix,,0,0,0,,Everyone's happy with your cooking.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.80,0:01:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your cooking tastes really good.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.60,0:01:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.95,0:01:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.55,0:01:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.80,0:01:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go wake everyone up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.10,0:02:05.50,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Repeating a yesterday filled with scrapes,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:10.30,op/ed,,0,0,0,,We clear the path to a hopeful tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:25.40,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I wonder what remains
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:28.60,op/ed,,0,0,0,,in both these tiny hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:34.95,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The voice I raised upwards scattered into the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.95,0:02:38.25,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The reality I've gamed is hazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:41.35,op/ed,,0,0,0,,and even if I can't see ahead of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:44.65,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I can keep moving forward on this long road
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.65,0:02:48.75,op/ed,,0,0,0,,if I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:55.00,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Connecting a bond covered in dust,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:03:01.35,op/ed,,0,0,0,,We join back to back in the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:07.80,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Repeating an answer full of mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:15.80,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I will reach out my hands to seek the light, again and again.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.00,0:03:46.25,Alt,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.00,0:03:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're very sorry.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.05,0:03:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It was an accident.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,An unfortunate accident!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.90,0:04:02.35,fix,,0,0,0,,How does a wall just break?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.35,0:04:05.65,fix,,0,0,0,,How... the heck am I supposed to know?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.65,0:04:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.60,0:04:08.05,Alt,,0,0,0,,Idiot, leave it!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.05,0:04:09.40,Alt,,0,0,0,,Just apologize!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.75,0:04:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like we saw anything.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.80,0:04:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit fussing.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.30,0:04:14.10,fix,,0,0,0,,You were trying to!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.20,fix,,0,0,0,,That's a crime!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.20,0:04:16.35,fix,,0,0,0,,I'll call the police!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.35,0:04:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There ain't any in this town!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.25,0:04:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you bring your hand towels in with you, anyway?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not supposed to.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.10,0:04:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little more and... damn.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.75,0:04:27.20,fix,,0,0,0,,How do you know this?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.20,0:04:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.15,0:04:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It... It's not like I-I'd want to l-look at a flat-chested girl like you!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.95,0:04:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me flat-chested!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.80,0:04:44.05,fix,,0,0,0,,Tell the truth. I won't get mad if you say it now.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.70,0:04:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.65,0:04:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...when I tried to climb the bath house wall, it broke.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.40,0:04:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It just means we were too inexperienced.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The wall and us.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.65,0:04:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You said you wouldn't get mad!
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.55,0:04:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I didn't see anything anyway.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.90,0:05:01.65,Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm never going to talk to you again!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.45,0:05:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.10,0:05:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still a little warm.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.80,0:05:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We might catch up to them.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.05,0:05:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Found them.
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.65,0:06:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Two... no, maybe three.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.50,0:06:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a lone poplin{boblin}, huh.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.45,0:06:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you mean "goblin" not "poplin{boblin}."
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.45,0:06:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.35,0:06:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.05,0:06:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It might take a while for Shihoru.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's okay if it's you.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.35,0:06:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying it would be okay if it were you who saw.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that even if you did, you would apologize...
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.60,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not that just because you apologized, it's okay either...
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.25,0:06:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's seen is seen...
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.10,0:06:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just repeating "seen" a lot...
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.35,0:06:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what's okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the person to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.60,0:06:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it wasn't right, huh.
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.25,0:06:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.00,0:07:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't right, Haru-kun.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.55,0:07:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.45,0:07:08.95,fix,,0,0,0,,So what will we do?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.95,0:07:10.45,fix,,0,0,0,,"What to do"?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.45,0:07:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do is go back to Ortana.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Gray pains but all for vain, huh.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.25,0:07:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You meant, "great pains but all in vain," right?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.55,0:07:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.35,0:07:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I remember it wrong?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.85,0:07:25.75,fix,,0,0,0,,It happens.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.90,0:07:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No earnings today.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.75,0:07:32.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,The next day...
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.30,0:07:34.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,...the day after...
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.45,0:07:37.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,...and the day after that...
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,...we barely earned anything.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.40,0:07:45.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,When I say barely, I mean close to nothing.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.40,0:07:49.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,Well, to be honest, we made nothing.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.75,0:07:54.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,The clothes we started off with quickly began to wear down.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.20,0:08:00.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,Well, they weren't made to withstand\Nhiking mountain trails and fighting goblins.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.30,0:08:04.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,So we do what we can to make them last, but...
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.10,0:08:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd give anything for new underwear...
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.80,0:08:12.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,But the clothes in this world are expensive.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.10,0:08:17.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,At least, because we're so poor we can't buy anything.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.45,0:08:20.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,We can't even buy underwear.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.05,0:08:24.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,So at night, we wash them and sleep without them.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.50,0:08:27.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,Then in the morning, we put them on under our equipment.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.55,0:08:30.35,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's better than no underwear at all.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.35,0:08:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.05,0:08:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My goal tomorrow is to defeat a goblin and buy new underwear.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.55,0:08:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.65,0:08:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done now.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,I smelled a faintly sweet scent.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.40,0:08:57.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.65,0:08:59.50,fix_it,,0,0,0,,We have been going without underwear...
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.10,0:09:00.95,fix_it,,0,0,0,,...and the girls?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.20,0:09:17.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,I'll sink down to Ranta's level.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.05,0:09:29.60,fix,,0,0,0,,Oh... I'm, uh...
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.60,0:09:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Haru-kun.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.35,0:09:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good night.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.15,0:09:37.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,Not good.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.00,0:09:39.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's not good if they're dressed like that.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.00,0:09:42.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's just too much if they wander around the lodging like that.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.00,0:09:44.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,Too much. It's just too much!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.20,0:09:45.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,They're too vulnerable!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.75,fix_it,,0,0,0,,Th-This isn't good, I'll really be on the same—
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.90,0:09:48.25,Alt,,0,0,0,,What're doing, Haruhiro?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.75,0:09:50.25,fix,,0,0,0,,No. Nothing.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.20,0:09:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The heck.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.05,0:09:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this rain.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.50,0:09:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's going to dry even if you wash them.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.30,0:09:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you wash stuff tomorrow?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.60,0:10:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if the rain will let up tomorrow.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.95,0:10:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the one who told me to wash my clothes\Nonce in a while 'cause they stink, Parupiro.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.10,0:10:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm trying to say is, I regret washing my stuff today.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.50,0:10:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.65,0:10:15.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,I can't let King Shameless here get near the girls right now.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.80,0:10:18.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,This sense of duty drove me to act.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.70,0:10:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right. It's a pain, anyway.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.15,0:10:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Right?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.45,0:10:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking maybe the girls were there, muhaha.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.60,0:10:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't "muhaha" me.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.90,0:10:34.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,The way they're dressed is too tempting.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.80,0:10:36.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,I've got to tell them.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.85,0:10:38.85,Italics,,0,0,0,,Or should I...?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.55,0:10:42.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,No! I'll tell them.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.15,0:10:48.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,This is Damuro.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.45,0:10:50.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,They say it was the second city of the Arabakia Kingdom.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.70,0:10:53.85,fix_it,,0,0,0,,It was much bigger city than Ortana.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.85,0:10:57.85,fix_it,,0,0,0,,Currently Damuro was a base for goblins.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.35,0:11:02.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,Goblins found near the new city area are numerous and strong.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.90,0:11:04.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,Too difficult for us to defeat.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.35,0:11:10.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,That's why we're going to the old city area\Nto target goblins separated from their groups.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.40,0:11:19.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,That said, compared to the forest, we have\Nmore encounters, so it's still dangerous.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,One goblin. Looks like {he's }sleeping.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.85,0:11:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's do it.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.70,0:11:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Moguzo's armor will make sound,\Nso Haruhiro, Ranta, and I will approach first.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.10,0:11:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can close in on the goblin without\Nwaking him, the three of us will finish him.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.35,0:11:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If we wake him, Yume, use your bow.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.60,0:11:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shihoru, back us up with magic from a distance.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.90,0:11:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Moguzo, you'll run to the front.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.00,0:11:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If it becomes a head-on fight,\Nwe'll use the same formation as before.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.55,0:11:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll surround him, so he can't get away.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.10,0:11:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't back away!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.85,0:12:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.20,0:12:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it dead?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.45,0:12:18.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's so easy... to attack them in their sleep.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.05,0:12:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get a claw or something.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.00,0:12:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice, Vice.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.80,0:12:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is our best record yet.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.75,0:12:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only our second time, though.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.50,0:12:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Four silvers.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.90,0:12:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah...
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.90,0:12:35.90,fix,,0,0,0,,It's not over yet.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.15,0:12:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We were lucky that it was easy today,\Nbut it won't always be like this.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.35,0:12:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your guard up and look for our next target.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.80,0:12:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, don't be such a killjoy.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.40,0:12:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We just had a huge win, thanks to me!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.50,0:12:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We should celebrate these times!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.20,0:12:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.90,0:12:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind enjoying it.
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.05,0:13:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You were a big help, too.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.80,0:13:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.85,0:13:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I really seem like a Dark Knight\Nwhen I wore a cruel smile as I stabbed the gob?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.95,0:13:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you were just as worked up as usual.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.80,0:13:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.55,0:13:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I got him good without a hitch!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.75,0:13:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are your eyes?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.15,0:13:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see them, right there!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.90,0:13:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes are such small slits, I barely noticed them!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.75,0:13:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, this again?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.70,0:13:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,At least react to it!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.64,0:13:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just say something, you gonna leave me hanging?!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.50,0:13:26.50,Alt,,0,0,0,,How many times is it now?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.50,0:13:27.70,Alt,,0,0,0,,It's getting annoying!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.30,0:13:28.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,We defeated an enemy.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.00,0:13:30.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,And earned money.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.80,0:13:32.95,fix_it,,0,0,0,,Party's mood lightened again.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.15,0:13:37.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,Everybody was probably on edge,\Nbecause they were worried, too.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.15,0:13:46.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,Before we know it, maybe we'll be thinking\Nand acting like Volunteer Soldiers.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.75,0:13:58.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,After that, we targeted lone goblins and defeated them.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.55,0:14:03.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,In Damuro, we sometimes encountered groups of five or more.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.90,0:14:07.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,A pair was hard enough, so five was out of the question.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.60,0:14:14.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,But still, we enjoyed the task of walking\Naround the old town and sketching out a map.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.70,0:14:18.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,We'd go explore places we hadn't been to yet.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.35,0:14:22.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,With that, we had a goal set,\Nso we learned our way around, too.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.30,0:14:27.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,We'd get nervous when we stepped into new areas.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.35,0:14:31.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,And we felt a little better in places we had mapped already.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be thirty coppers.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.25,0:14:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.45,0:14:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't these secondhand?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.95,0:14:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd consider it for fifteen coppers.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.55,0:14:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Brand new, it'd go for a hundred coppers.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.30,0:14:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty-eight coppers.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.80,0:14:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd go as far as twenty coppers.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.10,0:14:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have other things to buy.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.10,0:14:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty-five coppers.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.10,0:14:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go lower than that.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.15,0:14:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take it.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.45,0:14:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray!{Whoo-hoo!}
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.95,0:15:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! This is so freakin' good!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.60,0:15:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it called again?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.20,0:15:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's soruzo, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.30,0:15:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yum, soruzo's so good!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.90,0:15:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we get another order?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.30,0:15:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Comin' right up!
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shihoru?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.80,0:15:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.45,0:15:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... still not...
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.80,0:15:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.95,0:15:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you actually want him to talk to you?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.70,0:15:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There were a lot of nicks in the blade, huh.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.65,0:16:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You noticed?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.40,0:16:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Before anything else, I've got to\Nkeep my weapons in good condition.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.95,0:16:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Or else I feel uneasy.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.70,0:16:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I get that.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.70,0:16:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,With thoughts like these, do you think we've become influenced by Volunteer Soldiers too much?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.30,0:16:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Influenced or not...
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...we {\i1}are{\i0} Volunteer Soldiers, you know.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.20,0:16:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just trainees, though.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.20,0:16:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nice.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.55,0:16:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranta-kun kept haggling, so it was pretty hectic.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.30,0:16:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid, it's common sense to haggle.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.95,0:16:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That was nothing.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.35,0:16:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's too much, the food's going\Nto go bad before we can finish it.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.90,0:16:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If it rots, I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.05,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to buy weapons, clothes, and food...
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.95,0:16:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I was thinking we could keep spending to\Na minimum, so we could try learning new skills.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.10,0:16:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.20,0:16:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If I sharpen my Dark Knight blade skills,\Nit might be too much to handle!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.30,0:16:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, you only have one skill right now.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.50,0:16:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.95,0:16:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to polish up that one skill all the way!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.85,0:17:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Until it shines with dark light!
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you buy that, too?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.15,0:17:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I made this.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.50,0:17:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You carved that?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.55,0:17:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more deft than you look, Moguzo.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.45,0:17:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You could sell that.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.25,0:17:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that wasn't my intention...
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.75,0:17:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Carving's relaxing for me.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.80,0:17:15.70,fix,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.45,0:17:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yume and them might like it.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What made you think of Yume just now?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.65,0:17:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought they might like it.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.70,0:17:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what Haru-kun said?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.35,0:17:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"If we earn a little extra...
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.75,0:17:38.10,fix,,0,0,0,,...wouldn't that be nice to have\Nclothes for wearing indoors, too?"
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.95,0:17:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.65,0:17:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That... would be nice.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.15,0:17:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.95,0:17:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.45,0:17:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shihoru, that hair clip is super cute.
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.00,0:17:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.10,0:17:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You... think so?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.75,0:18:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shihoru, I know you haven't been\Ntalking to the guys this whole time.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.05,0:18:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think it's about time that you could try, just a little bit.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.45,0:18:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.15,0:18:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't have to try.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.40,0:18:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I get worried when you're always quiet, too.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.50,0:18:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.80,0:18:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.05,0:18:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not too good with words.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.75,0:18:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.25,0:18:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, thanks.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.55,0:18:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That was unexpected.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.40,0:19:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.30,0:19:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I was actually about to say something completely different.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.10,0:19:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.45,0:19:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who is grateful.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.90,0:19:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're grateful?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.65,0:19:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.95,0:19:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because... you're all willing to be my friends.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.60,0:19:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,For that, I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.65,0:19:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds a little fake when I say it like this.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.35,0:19:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I believe you.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.55,0:19:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.90,0:19:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I say this...
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.65,0:19:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who's been helping us.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.45,0:19:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you weren't here, we'd be in bad shape.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.35,0:19:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Worst case, we might not even be alive.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.40,0:19:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Same goes here.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.70,0:19:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you guys weren't here, I don't know\Nwhat would have happened to me.
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.60,0:19:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't live in this world alone, no matter how you look at it.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.90,0:20:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you... uh...
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.25,0:20:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to take this the wrong way...
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.35,0:20:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...but don't you think you could\Nhave made a lot of other friends?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.15,0:20:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You could just ask for a favor and\Nsee if you could join their party.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.30,0:20:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think of that.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.35,0:20:24.30,fix,,0,0,0,,I don't think I like that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.80,0:20:26.55,fix,,0,0,0,,To ask others for favors.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.50,0:20:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I was bad at dealing with hierarchical relationships.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.60,0:20:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably was, too.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.50,0:20:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of feel like... I'm not the kind of\Nperson people usually treat as a friend.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.65,0:20:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think...
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.50,0:20:49.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,...that's true.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.65,0:20:53.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,That's just what I think, but I can't back it up.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.50,0:20:57.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's true that I only know the Manato in this world.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.45,0:21:00.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.15,0:21:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter what you were like before.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.05,0:21:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody cares.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.20,0:21:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Manato in this world is our friend and leader.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.85,0:21:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We need you here.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.10,0:21:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's sleep.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.85,0:21:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an early day tomorrow.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.50,0:21:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.85,0:21:39.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,I wasn't sure if I wanted to see the\Nexpression on his face right now.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.15,0:21:45.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,Day twenty-three in Grimgar.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.95,Italics,,0,0,0,,I've gotten used to the red moon.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.45,0:21:54.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,People can get used to any kind of environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:56.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,.At least...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:58.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,...I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.90,0:22:23.20,op/ed,,0,0,0,,When I try touching
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.30,0:22:29.45,op/ed,,0,0,0,,the dry air after a rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:36.10,op/ed,,0,0,0,,like a sprouting flower,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.10,0:22:42.40,op/ed,,0,0,0,,fragments of memories overflow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:55.05,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The warmth you gave this hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.05,0:23:03.85,op/ed,,0,0,0,,led me to a future I can treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.85,0:23:06.60,op/ed,,0,0,0,,always.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.60,0:23:13.80,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I chased your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.80,0:23:19.45,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I wonder when you became so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.45,0:23:26.40,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I will probably find what I searched the vast world for
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.40,0:23:33.95,op/ed,,0,0,0,,at the end of this journey.
